{"tid":234753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【相距一天】九龍灣色魔昨凌晨姦劫22歲女學生 兩事非同日發生","createTime":"2017-05-08T13:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T13:53:03.000Z","uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10b7071fd8f1cf81c36bcc993318b13ba922c235","tid":234753,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"觀塘道九龍灣港鐵站B出口對開的行人天橋及空地，前日凌晨發生22歲女學生遭姦劫案，警方今日凌晨才向傳媒公布事件，傳媒即時作出跟進報道。而警方昨晚在姦劫案現場附近的觀塘區一幢工廈，協助入境處搜查演出場地Hidden Agenda，行動至今日凌晨才結束。由於姦劫案事隔一天公布，故與Hidden Agenda被查事件被傳媒同日報道，有網民質疑事件導致警力分散讓色魔有機可乘。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本報就網民的疑問向警方查詢，獲警方方回覆指，姦劫案於昨日（7日）凌晨零時許發生，女事主於同日早上6時許報警；至於協助入境處到Hidden Agenda執法，則是昨晚（8日）深夜11時許開始至今日凌晨時分，時間相差近一天，相信不涉警力分散讓色魔有機可乘問題。<br />\n<br />\n至於警方為何發生姦劫案要待至今日凌晨始公布？據消息稱，警方在昨早接獲女事主報案，經調查後，因估計色魔會同日再次犯案或出現於案發現場，所以派員在現場一帶埋伏監視守候，但至今日凌晨仍不見色魔影蹤，為顧及市民安全決定將案件公開，讓市民提防。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170508/s00001/1494247871706#sthash.tz3olYik.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170508%2Fs00001%2F1494247871706%23sthash.tz3olYik.dpuf&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=601c19f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170508%2Fs00001%2F1494247871706%23sthash.tz3olYik.dpuf&h=75600e25\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170508/s00001/1494247871706#sthash.tz3olYik.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"b50d755f7a4c484709657fcf84e2e41cc8da7746","tid":234753,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170508/s00001/11b61960d961173ac1d8e35ab18038f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170508%2Fs00001%2F11b61960d961173ac1d8e35ab18038f0.jpg&h=af1994de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28ba72fd00b5cde0eb9f44a2a31a35c0599fb959","tid":234753,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:35:42.000Z","msg":"唔公布一定有hidden agenda"},{"pid":"2dba831b10af9f6b5d6f4cbe91943b706365a1df","tid":234753,"uid":23918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"咁啲猶差係今日去現場搜證...?"},{"pid":"0735a8a463cd50c29065fe85e8c250295074ecca","tid":234753,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁啲猶差係今日去現場搜證...?</blockquote><br />\n不能說的"},{"pid":"bf5f9baa84410b5358131438ff9e751aa6719266","tid":234753,"uid":68491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁啲猶差係今日去現場搜證...?</blockquote><br />\n不能說的</blockquote><br />\n唔係今日唔通琴日?<br />\n唔係比連登仔知道左呢單野，佢地都唔會去啦"},{"pid":"9fcaa99fbd905d4f0f3612e785b27162f9363f2c","tid":234753,"uid":73422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"又炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}